wednesday: Wednesday, August 29 at the [Royal Academy](http://academieroyale.be), those who think about the uses and seek to generalize them as much as to particularize them, the researchers in education on the uses of the digital, the teachers who want to share their practices, will meet in a conference for exchange of experiences and research presentations. Childcare solutions with activities will be organized so that all parents can participate.
