expo_about:

During the coffee breaks and meals, all the structures (associations, public institutions, schools, commercial companies ...) active in the digital education sector in Belgium and elsewhere represented during the conference, will present their achievements in the [exhibition](/exposition).

This will be accessible mainly during coffee breaks and lunch and dinner.

It will be an opportunity for teachers, their directorates, elected representatives and their teams, as well as for public authorities to become acquainted with the great diversity of digital actors in the field of education. They will be able to assist and help schools in a mission of support and training for the many uses of digital technology.
---
partners_about:

The partners of the conference are all the actors who consider that the question is important and who wish to contribute to the extent of their means. They are Belgian and foreign, most associative. Some provide essential financial support, the others participate in the promotion and dissemination of information around the conference, are members of the organizing committee of the conference, supervise workshops ...

Many participate in the [exhibition](/exposition) of [Monday 27](/lundi-27-aout).
